Module org.monarchinitiative.phenol.analysis
Package org.monarchinitiative.phenol.analysis.scoredist

Class H2ScoreDistributionReader

java.lang.Object
org.monarchinitiative.phenol.analysis.scoredist.H2ScoreDistributionReader
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, AutoCloseable, ScoreDistributionReader
public class H2ScoreDistributionReader extends Object implements ScoreDistributionReader
Read score distributions from H2 database.

H2 Dependency Notes

The class itself only uses JDBC. Thus, the ontolib module does not depend on H2 via maven but your calling code has to depend on H2.

Author:
Manuel Holtgrewe
